    "summary": "[February FOHE Coffee Hour] - Reimagining Admissions",
    "description": "<p>Join us for a conversation about <b>reimagining college admissions</b> \u2013 spotlighting the <a href=\"https://www.luminafoundation.org/admissions-redesign/\" target=\"_blank\">Lumina Foundation</a>\u2019s <a href=\"https://www.luminafoundation.org/admissions-redesign/\">Great Admissions Redesign work</a>,\u00a0with <a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://www.linkedin.com/in/melaniewheath/\">Melanie Heath</a> (Strategy Director for Access, Lumina Foundation), <a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://www.linkedin.com/in/juliaelizabethdixon/\">Julia Dixon</a> (Founder/CEO, <a href=\"https://www.esai.ai/\">ESAI</a>), and <a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://www.gse.harvard.edu/directory/faculty/richard-weissbourd\">Richard Weissbourd</a> (Senior Lecturer, Harvard Graduate School of Education).</p><br>-------<br><br><a href=\"https://www.fohe.org/\" target=\"_blank\"><u><u><u><u><u><u><u><u><u><u><u>FOHE</u></u></u></u></u></u></u></u></u></u></u></a>\u00a0Coffee Hour is 12-1pm Eastern Time on the last Wednesday of every month.<br><br>We'll send out a calendar hold near the beginning of each month with the details for that month's session.<br><br>Don't forget to check out the ongoing conversations on FOHE's\u00a0<a href=\"https://futureofhighered.slack.com/\" target=\"_blank\"><u><u><u><u><u><u><u><u><u><u><u><u><u>Slack</u></u></u></u></u></u></u></u></u></u></u></u></u></a>.",
